        Consists of all the parameters of this class to create a full Employee Node object
        Parameters:
        first_name - First name of the employee
        last_name - Last name of the employee
        name - Deconstructed name of the employee from the EmployeeManager.java
        middle_name - Middle name of the employee
        former_name - Former name of the employee
        preferred_name - Preferred name of the employee
        email - Business email of the employee
        title - Current position of the employee
        company - Company the employee currently works at
        department_name - Department name of the employee
        payroll_department - Payroll department of the employee
        location - Where the employee is currently located
        month - Birth month of the employee
        day - Birth day of the employee
        gender - Sex of the employee
        newManager - Manager object of the employee
        new_employee_number - Employee Id of the employee
        manager_employeeNumber - Employee's manager's employee Id
        initial_manager_name - Initial name of the employee's manager

      • EmployeeNode

        EmployeeNode​(java.lang.String name,
             java.lang.String department_name,
             EmployeeNode newManager,
             java.lang.String new_employee_number)
        An EmployeeNode object with only some of its attributes. Mainly used to create temperory manager or temperory employee objects
        Parameters:
        name - Deconstructed name of the employee from the EmployeeManager.java
        department_name - Department name of the employee
        newManager - Manager object of the employee
        new_employee_number - Employee Id of the employee
